data.description: $8,000 Seller concession /closing cost assistance. MOTIVATED SELLER: BRING ALL OFFERS Available for lease to own using a free application at min. 500 credit score or purchase. with lease, security Deposit is refundable and 10% of monthly rent is held in escrow and can be applied towards down payment of lease to own option.***Nestled in a serene and well-kept neighborhood in Conyers, Georgia, this charming and spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bath home, two car attached garage offers the perfect blend of comfort and traditional elegance. With no HOA restrictions, you'll have the freedom to make this house your own. The expansive backyard is a true oasis, providing ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation. The inviting living area welcomes you with warm natural light, creating a cozy atmosphere that resonates throughout the home.The kitchen boasts a classic design with modern amenities, featuring ample counter space, and a eat in kitchen area. The dining area, seamlessly connected to the kitchen as well as the living room for ideal entertainment.The spacious primary suite is a retreat unto itself, complete with an en-suite bathroom for privacy and convenience.Three additional well-appointed bedrooms provide versatility for guests, home offices, or hobbies. The large backyard is a blank canvas for outdoor enthusiasts, ready to accommodate your landscaping dreams, gardening ventures, or even the installation of a pool.Situated in a desirable Conyers neighborhood, this home offers a tranquil suburban lifestyle while still being conveniently close to urban amenities. Enjoy easy access to local schools, parks, shopping centers, and dining options, making every day a delightful experience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming traditional house your forever home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and envision the possibilities that await you in this lovely Conyers property.
